HEADWORD: Mangonist
<hw>Man"go*nist</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One
who mangonizes.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A slave dealer; also, a strumpet.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mangonize</ent>⟦br⟧
